properties.Name: MineMeasuredResource
properties.Description: Mine Measured resources are the indicated mine resources that have undergone enough additional sampling that a geologist or team of geologists have declared them to be an acceptable estimate with a high degree of confidence regarding the product grade, tonnage, shape, densities, physical characteristics and mineral content of the mineral occurrence.

Columns.Name: ProductId

Columns.Name: UnitOfMeasureId

Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding a mine measured resource.
